						<div class="postbody"><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">nmi_count = $10 ; one byte in zero-page, location up to you<br /><br />nmi:&nbsp; inc nmi_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; rti<br /><br />wait_nmi:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; lda nmi_count<br />loop: cmp nmi_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; beq loop<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; rts</div><br /><br />By not modifying nmi_count outside of NMI, other code can use it for timing, i.e.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; lda nmi_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; cmp next_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; beq one_second_passed<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ...<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br />one_second_passed:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; clc&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; update next_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; adc #60<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; sta next_count<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ...</div></div>

